[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0070","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0070.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0419","title":"Microsoft Exchange SMTP Service 4xx 错误代码拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange Server 的 SMTP 服务在处理邮件投递时存在拒绝服务漏洞。当 SMTP 服务向目标邮件服务器发送邮件并收到 4xx 临时错误响应码时，会快速且反复地重试投递该邮件，导致系统资源被大量消耗，最终造成邮件服务不可用。攻击者可通过配置邮件服务器返回 4xx 状态码来触发此漏洞，影响 Exchange Server 的邮件处理功能。该漏洞属于早期发现的拒绝服务类问题，利用难度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0419"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:21.433","remediation":"建议安装 Microsoft Exchange Server 5.5 Service Pack 2 或更高版本，该更新修复了 SMTP 服务在收到 4xx 错误码时陷入死循环导致拒绝服务的问题。临时缓解措施可在 SMTP 虚拟服务器上启用连接限制和超时设置，限制同一来源的并发连接数。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0419","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0419.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0419","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0419.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0419.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3r6q-4vvg-jmx9/GHSA-3r6q-4vvg-jmx9.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0419.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000553.txt","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/windows.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0070.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0061","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0061.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0414","title":"Linux Kernel TCP 欺骗漏洞","description":"Linux 内核 2.0.36 之前版本的 TCP 协议栈存在盲欺骗漏洞。远程攻击者可在未完成完整 TCP 三次握手前，通过预测 TCP 序列号向应用层注入伪造数据，绕过连接建立验证机制。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.0.30 至 2.0.37 版本，攻击者无需处于中间人位置即可实施盲注入攻击，可能导致数据篡改或会话劫持。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0414"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:20.800","remediation":"升级至 Linux 内核 2.0.36 或更高版本以修复 TCP 握手机制缺陷；若无法升级内核，启用 TCP syncookies（`echo 1 > /proc/sys/net/ipv4/tcp_syncookies`）并配置 iptables 限制入站 TCP 连接速率以降低欺骗攻击风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0414","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0414.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0414","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0414.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0414.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-33wp-c8x6-pv3w/GHSA-33wp-c8x6-pv3w.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-0414.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000552.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0061.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0060","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0060.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0413","title":"SGI IRIX X Server 字体路径缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 操作系统 X Window System 服务器在处理字体路径时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过构造恶意的字体路径参数触发该漏洞，覆盖内存中的关键数据，从而获取系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 系统，攻击者需要拥有本地访问权限才能利用。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0413"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:20.670","remediation":"安装 SGI 安全公告 19990301-01-PX 提供的对应补丁，或升级到包含该修复的 IRIX 版本。鉴于 SGI 已停止运营且 IRIX 已终止支持多年，建议将仍在运行的 IRIX 系统迁移至受支持的操作系统；若无法迁移，应严格限制本地登录权限、最小化可访问 X 服务器的用户范围，并禁用不必要的 X 字体服务以降低利用面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0060.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0038","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0038.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0386","title":"Microsoft FrontPage Personal Web Server 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Microsoft FrontPage Personal Web Server 1.0 及 4.0 存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的非标准 URL 请求，突破路径限制访问服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响运行 Personal Web Server 的 Windows 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可实施利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0386"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:17.143","remediation":"升级到 Microsoft Personal Web Server 更高版本，或改用 IIS 替代 FrontPage PWS 根除风险。如无法升级，在 IIS 管理器中禁用非标准 URL 解析，并部署 URLScan 安全工具过滤 `../../` 等目录遍历字符，同时限制 WEB 目录执行权限为纯脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/111","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-010","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19753","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0386.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0386","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0386.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0386.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/951.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-frontpage.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/M/mspws_dotdotdot.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0038.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0018","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0018.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0261","title":"NetManage Chameleon SMTPd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NetManage Chameleon SMTPd 服务存在多处缓冲区溢出漏洞，源于对 HELO 和 HELP 等 SMTP 命令输入长度缺乏有效边界检查。远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标 SMTP 端口发送超长命令（如 HELO 后跟超过 471 字符的主机名），触发缓冲区溢出导致服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台上的 Chameleon 4.5 及 UnixLink 97 版本，CVSS v2 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0261"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.477","remediation":"该漏洞影响 Netmanage Chameleon 4.5 及 Unixlink 97 的 SMTPd 服务（Windows NT 平台），由于产品早已停止维护且厂商未发布补丁，建议升级迁移至受支持的 SMTP 服务器（如 Exchange Server、Postfix 等）。若暂时无法迁移，应在防火墙限制对 TCP 25 端口的访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接；同时监控 SMTP 服务的异常崩溃日志以及时发现攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.insecure.org/sploits/netmanage.chameleon.overflows.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0261.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0261","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0261.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0261.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0261.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9v5m-hg7x-6gfx/GHSA-9v5m-hg7x-6gfx.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0261.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2387/info.html","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0018.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0013","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0013.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0223","title":"Sun Solaris syslogd 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统 syslogd 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，当远程主机向目标 Solaris 系统发送 syslog 消息时，若该主机缺少反向 DNS（PTR）记录，syslogd 在处理过程中会发生崩溃，导致系统日志服务中断。攻击者无需认证即可利用此漏洞，持续发送此类消息可使 syslogd 反复崩溃，影响系统日志记录功能。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0223"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.797","remediation":"升级 Solaris 系统至包含此补丁的版本（如 Solaris 2.6 及以上），或在 /etc/syslog.conf 中禁用反向 DNS 解析功能；同时建议在防火墙层面限制外部主机向 UDP 514 端口发送 syslog 消息，防止未授权来源触发崩溃。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.Sun.COM/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?patchid=103291&collection=fpatches","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1878"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0013.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0012","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0012.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0222","title":"Cisco IOS Web Server 长URL拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 路由器的 Web 服务器组件存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标设备发送超长 URL 即可触发缓冲区溢出，导致 IOS 进程崩溃并迫使路由器重新启动，造成网络服务中断。该漏洞影响启用 HTTP 服务的 Cisco IOS 设备，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。缓解措施为禁用不必要的 HTTP 服务或通过访问控制列表限制来源 IP。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0222"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.680","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至修复版本（如 11.2(18)、12.0(11) 及以上），或禁用 HTTP 服务：全局配置模式下执行 `no ip http server`。如需保留 HTTP 服务，通过 `ip http access-class` 配合 ACL 限制可信管理源地址，并在接口上应用 `ip access-group` 过滤对 80 端口的非授权访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/60159","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0222.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0222","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0222.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0222.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0222.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0222.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8cfdaab2997679f3e193ea9539f778b75d8c9d41/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0012.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0012.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0012.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0011","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0011.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0221","title":"Lucent Ascend 路由器远程管理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Lucent Ascend 路由器远程管理服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，攻击者可通过向目标路由器的 150 端口（远程管理端口）发送特制数据包，导致路由器服务崩溃或无法响应正常请求。该漏洞影响 Lucent Ascend 系列路由器，无需身份认证即可远程触发，危害等级中危。官方已发布固件更新修复此漏洞，建议用户升级至最新版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0221"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.547","remediation":"在防火墙或访问控制列表（ACL）中限制对 TCP/UDP 150 端口的访问，仅允许 trusted 管理 IP 连接。如无需远程管理功能，建议在路由器配置中禁用远程管理服务（no remote-management）。若设备仍在使用，应升级至供应商支持的最新固件版本，或替换为受支持的现代路由器设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0221","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0221.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0221.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0221","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0221.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0221.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-635x-qr4g-qqp3/GHSA-635x-qr4g-qqp3.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0221.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80896/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0011.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0111","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0111.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0438","title":"Ramp Networks WebRamp 1.0 UDP数据包拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Ramp Networks WebRamp 1.0 设备存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标设备的 UDP 5353 端口发送特制恶意数据包，触发设备 IP 地址被异常修改，导致网络连接中断。该漏洞利用难度较低，仅需构造简单的 UDP 报文即可实现攻击，影响 WebRamp 全系版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0438"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"在防火墙上配置规则阻止外部来源对 UDP 5353 端口的访问，防止恶意 UDP 包篡改设备 IP 地址。由于 Ramp Networks 已被收购且该产品已停止维护，建议更换为仍在支持周期内的同类网络设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0438"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0111.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0088","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0088.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0431","title":"Linux Kernel 2.2.3 及更早版本 IP 分段处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux 内核 2.2.3 及更早版本的 IP 协议栈在处理分片数据包时存在缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可发送特制的零长度 IP 分片报文，导致目标系统内核在处理分片重组时出现异常，进而触发系统崩溃或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.1.89 至 2.2.16 版本，攻击者只需发送少量恶意分片数据包即可完成利用，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0431"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb","nvd"],"published":"1999-03-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.2.4 或更高版本，该版本已修复零长度 IP 分片导致的拒绝服务漏洞。如无法升级，可在防火墙上配置规则丢弃非法分片数据包作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0431","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0431","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0431.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6594-47rj-5vcw/GHSA-6594-47rj-5vcw.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0088.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0036","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0036.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0381","title":"Super Syslog 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Super 3.11.6 及之前版本的 syslog 工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 syslog 发送超长日志消息触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖内存中的关键数据，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Debian 2.0 系统，攻击者需要拥有本地账户才能利用，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0381"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-26","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 super 软件包至 3.12.0 或更高版本，该版本修复了 syslog 函数中的缓冲区溢出问题。对于仍运行 Debian 2.0 的系统，建议升级至受支持的 Debian 发行版，因为 Debian 2.0 已停止安全支持多年。如无法升级，限制本地用户对 super 程序的执行权限，仅允许受信任的管理员用户使用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/342","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=Pine.LNX.3.96.990225011801.12757A-100000%40eleet","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19270"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0036.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0156","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0156.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0483","title":"OpenBSD FFS和EXT2FS文件系统nlink值处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"OpenBSD 的 FFS 和 EXT2FS 文件系统实现中存在拒绝服务漏洞。由于内核在处理文件 nlink 值（硬链接计数）时未做边界检查，当本地用户创建超过 65535 个硬链接时，nlink 值会溢出并触发内核崩溃，导致系统拒绝服务。攻击者需要本地 shell 权限即可利用，无需特殊权限。该漏洞影响早期版本的 OpenBSD 操作系统。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0483"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:29.640","remediation":"升级 OpenBSD 至 2.5 或更高版本，或应用 2.4 errata 第 001 号（EXT2FS 补丁）和第 004 号（FFS link 补丁）源码补丁后重新编译内核。临时缓解措施可限制不可信用户的本地登录权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6129"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0156.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0052","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0052.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0408","title":"Cobalt RaQ 微服务器 shell 历史记录文件信息泄露漏洞","description":"Cobalt RaQ 微型服务器存在信息泄露漏洞，当用户通过交互式 Shell 会话登录系统时，生成的会话历史文件（如 .bash_history）默认权限为世界可读，且位于 Web 服务器可访问的目录下。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 Web 服务器直接读取这些文件，获取敏感信息（如命令历史、密码等），进而可能导致服务器被完全控制。该漏洞影响 Cobalt RaQ 系列微型服务器产品。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0408"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:19.997","remediation":"修改 /etc/profile 或 /etc/bashrc 中的 umask 设置为 077，确保新建文件默认仅属主可读写。同时配置 Apache 的 &lt;FilesMatch&gt; 规则拒绝访问 .bash_history 等点号开头的隐藏文件，并清理已存在的历史文件权限为 600。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/337","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0408.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0408","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0408.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0408.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xx49-8f9w-5r74/GHSA-xx49-8f9w-5r74.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0408.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--79fb0f29-9144-486d-9073-fd90218349d6.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0052.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0052.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0052.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0035","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0035.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0380","title":"SLMail 远程管理服务 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"SLMail 3.1 及 3.2 版本在启用远程管理服务（RAS）时存在不安全的文件访问漏洞。本地攻击者可将用户的 Finger 文件路径设置为指向任意目标文件，然后执行 finger 命令读取该文件内容，从而访问 NTFS 文件系统中的任意文件。该漏洞源于 SLMail 对 Finger 服务中文件路径处理不当，导致权限验证缺失，造成敏感信息泄露。攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0380"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:16.370","remediation":"升级 SLMail 至 4.0 或更新版本，该版本已修复 Finger File 路径遍历漏洞；如无法升级，禁用 Remote Administration Service (RAS) 组件，并限制本地用户对 Finger File 配置的写入权限。作为临时缓解措施，可移除 finger 服务或通过防火墙阻止 finger 端口 (79/TCP) 的外部访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91996412724720&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91999015212415&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92110501504997&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/497","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/5392"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0035.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1022","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1022.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1247","title":"HP HP-UX DCE/9000 摄像机组件本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 9.x 操作系统中 DCE/9000 环境的 HP Camera 组件存在权限提升漏洞，攻击者利用该漏洞可获取 root 权限。漏洞成因是 Camera 组件未正确限制权限访问，导致攻击者可通过特制请求提升至超级用户权限，完全控制目标系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1247"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:01.920","remediation":"升级 HP-UX 至 10.x 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，可移除或禁用 HP DCE/9000 的 Camera 组件（执行 `/usr/sbin/swremove HP-Camera`），并限制本地用户对 DCE 服务的访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/advisories/hpalert/006","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2061"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1022.toml"}]